    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set out on a journey through beautifully hand-drawn worlds in this turn-based puzzle adventure. Play as Sophia, a brave girl guided by a mysterious glowing pendant as she explores lands inspired by ancient Greek mythology in search of her lost father and her own inner courage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197650/extras/297b0211285688ddf0de6d05758386d2.poster.avif?t=1771195510\" width=550 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197650/extras/297b0211285688ddf0de6d05758386d2.webm?t=1771195510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197650/extras/297b0211285688ddf0de6d05758386d2.mp4?t=1771195510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197650/extras/86c73ac1226ac7f7eee51eef76911dfb.avif?t=1771195510\" width=1560 height=242 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your wits to overcome a variety of obstacles as you traverse beautifully hand-drawn worlds ruled by powerful deities like Medusa, Zeus, and Hades. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each realm presents unique challenges. In <strong>Medusa’s Lair</strong> carefully navigate her gaze. Face <strong>Zeus’s electrifying trials</strong> in the Sky Sanctuary and explore Hades’ underworld by blending in among spirits or even help <strong>Goddess Hera</strong> with her runaway peacock.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197650/extras/096c1e0bd1903479fccfd2924dfdde76.poster.avif?t=1771195510\" width=550 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197650/extras/096c1e0bd1903479fccfd2924dfdde76.webm?t=1771195510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197650/extras/096c1e0bd1903479fccfd2924dfdde76.mp4?t=1771195510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197650/extras/189d559bc10e316a8e01b66b821c36b9.avif?t=1771195510\" width=1560 height=242 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Along the way, Sophia encounters charming companions who will guide her, challenge her and even join in on the adventures. With each step, she grows closer to finding her father, overcoming challenges, and discovering that even the mightiest gods can be gentle at heart.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197650/extras/8363d2604d977c84ba7cc5f281ab82bc.poster.avif?t=1771195510\" width=550 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197650/extras/8363d2604d977c84ba7cc5f281ab82bc.webm?t=1771195510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197650/extras/8363d2604d977c84ba7cc5f281ab82bc.mp4?t=1771195510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197650/extras/bdedc18bc6e0589e323153d194f3425e.avif?t=1771195510\" width=1560 height=242 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Track down curious Little Rascals and collect ancient Relics hidden throughout each world. Exploration and curiosity are always rewarded.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197650/extras/80b8121d902035a81159deca52691394.poster.avif?t=1771195510\" width=550 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197650/extras/80b8121d902035a81159deca52691394.webm?t=1771195510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197650/extras/80b8121d902035a81159deca52691394.mp4?t=1771195510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Demo now available!</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play the first chapter of Sophia's adventure</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the Ancient Greek village of <strong>Soteris</strong> and the <strong>Wanderwoods</strong>, leading toward Athena's temple</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet <strong>friends</strong> who will help guide your way</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect mischievous <strong>Rascals</strong> and long lost <strong>Relics</strong> along each path </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full gamepad support and playable on Steam Deck</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Full Game Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 60 challenging and mythologically inspired turn-based path puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Four more beautifully hand-drawn worlds inspired by Greek mythology</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An overworld and tracking for all path achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A heartfelt story about courage, curiosity and overcoming our fears</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fun Steam Achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An Original Soundtrack that brings each world to life</p></li></ul>",
